Influences
----------

Rogue, by Toy, Wichman and Arnold, for the original gameplay concept.

Oryx LOFI fantasy tileset for the 8x8 tileset style.

Jeff Lait's Jacob's Matrix and subsequent games for the portal-based game
map architecture.

